#| "handle <emphasis>maildir</emphasis> folder names (nor can it handle "
#| "<emphasis>permissions</emphasis>, which can cause many other problems). "
#| "You have two choices. Either format your <acronym>USB</acronym> stick as "
#| "ext2 (in which case you should be aware it can't be read on &Windows; "
